stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initial
    Initial --> DateInput : User inputs date
    DateInput --> Validating : Validate date
    Validating --> Valid : Date is valid
    Validating --> Invalid : Date is invalid
    Valid --> Searching : Start search for data
    Searching --> Results : Display results
    Invalid --> DateInput : Prompt for valid date
    Results --> [*] : End of search